*[[何秀蘭|何秀蘭]]：前立法會議員、[[中西區_(香港)|中西區]]區議員<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hk.news.yahoo.com/070903/12/2ewwp.html |title=何秀蘭不參加立法會補選 |accessdate=2007-09-07 |archive-date=2007-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070907070204/http://hk.news.yahoo.com/070903/12/2ewwp.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
